name: Joe Biden I President of the USA I LoRA
description:
LEGAL NOTICE: This LoRA was not trained on real pictures of the President of the United States and only tries to mimic the look of Joe Biden.

No Recommended LoRA weight due to Inconsistency

Tested and works great with checkpoint:Deliberate/RealisticVision/

Works best with realistic/semi-realistic checkpoints.

Make sure to add "Joe Biden" to prompt,additonally "old man" if issues should persist.

Note: Turning the steps to a certain range (about 35-60) creates artifacts with some checkpoints and I couldn't figure out why.

Trained on 768x768 resolution.

NOT INTENDED FOR MALICIOUS USE

Feedback is welcome and appreciated, just like advice to improve.

Need help? write a comment!

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description:
Version 1.0 - First Release

Known Issues: Face artifacts with some checkpoints at certain step range (~35-60).
